758
01:05:52,465 --> 01:05:56,333
Then you too come.
- Yes, you come too. Come.

759
01:05:57,503 --> 01:06:01,439
Okay, if the neighbour comes and
sits with Zahira, I will come too.

760
01:06:02,041 --> 01:06:03,508
It'll be good for me to leave home too.

761
