He is like this.
- Yes, since childhood.

763
01:06:10,550 --> 01:06:13,348
He became like this after he
was wounded in the head once.

764
01:06:13,553 --> 01:06:17,353
Does he know? - What? -
That his father has died.

765
01:06:17,423 --> 01:06:18,515
