766
01:06:19,525 --> 01:06:20,492
Give me.

767
01:06:23,529 --> 01:06:26,432
Hanif, when did you start?

768
01:06:26,432 --> 01:06:27,524
Friend, I started this
since I was tensed.

769
01:06:28,467 --> 01:06:33,427
Hurry up, sit. We've to return
soon. - Be careful. - Let's go.

770
01:06:36,742 --> 01:06:39,575
Lucky, prepare four omelettes.
I will come in some time.

771
01:06:41,581 --> 01:06:43,549
Some people carry on
like nothing happened.

772
01:06:44,584 --> 01:06:47,519
Because they can.
- And we can't.

773
01:06:48,854 --> 01:06:50,446
That's why we must leave.

774
01:06:52,525 --> 01:06:55,426
Come, Mr. Sameer. After a long time.

775
01:06:55,995 --> 01:06:57,462
Lucky's night has become double lucky.

776
01:06:58,531 --> 01:07:02,399
Two delicious bun omelettes. -
One without chilli. - Correct.

777
01:07:02,501 --> 01:07:05,561
Very good. Very good.
- Shall we pack it? It's getting late.

778
01:07:06,539 --> 01:07:08,439
No, madam. Sit. Please sit.

779
01:07:08,574 --> 01:07:12,510
Come, let's eat it piping hot here. Sit.

780
01:07:15,281 --> 01:07:18,614
Lucky, how are you?
- Yes. Nothing, sir.

781
01:07:19,619 --> 01:07:22,486
These riots have ruined our business.

782
01:07:23,189 --> 01:07:26,283
I can't even ask the
shopkeeper for riot discount..

783
01:07:26,492 --> 01:07:27,584
..when things are so expensive.

784
01:07:30,062 --> 01:07:33,657
Don't worry. Your omelette is a
hit, forget about other things.

785
01:07:34,000 --> 01:07:39,461
What can I say, sir? I've to
feed the entire army for free.

786
