Just to stay here and that too alone.

787
01:07:42,141 --> 01:07:43,608
But where is Chhotya?

788
01:07:45,611 --> 01:07:48,512
He hasn't come since
the riots have started.

789
01:07:50,016 --> 01:07:51,483
May God keep him safe.

790
01:07:58,691 --> 01:08:02,559
Listen. We'll be fine in Delhi.

791
01:08:05,131 --> 01:08:08,589
A fresh start is always a good thing.
- Yes.

792
