I'm not joking. I'm truly a Muslim.

806
01:08:56,348 --> 01:08:57,372
Will you stop it, Sameer?

807
01:08:57,750 --> 01:09:02,210
Sir, such jokes are
dangerous at such times.

808
01:09:02,455 --> 01:09:07,290
You can't say anything.
You don't know when.. Sir.

809
01:09:07,393 --> 01:09:09,224
Come. Come. What will you have?

810
01:09:09,361 --> 01:09:11,226
Omelette, scrambled egg or boiled egg?

811
01:09:11,363 --> 01:09:12,421
Come on, wind up.

812
01:09:13,365 --> 01:09:14,389
There is going to be commotion today.

813
01:09:15,434 --> 01:09:18,232
And you two also move on.

814
01:09:19,438 --> 01:09:23,238
One minute, sir, I am
just finishing this.

815
01:09:23,943 --> 01:09:25,638
At such times, you must
not fulfil your wishes.

816
01:09:25,978 --> 01:09:29,106
Come on. You had enough.

817
01:09:31,550 --> 01:09:34,542
No, sir. We are going. ln
fact, we are leaving the city.

818
01:09:34,854 --> 01:09:36,481
He likes Lucky's omelette, that's why..

819
01:09:36,589 --> 01:09:38,420
For the last time.

820
01:09:38,891 --> 01:09:39,550
Come.

821
01:09:39,592 --> 01:09:40,616
What is your name you said?

822
01:09:40,826 --> 01:09:44,592
My name is Anuradha Desai
and this is my husband Sameer.

823
01:09:44,930 --> 01:09:46,557
Make Mr. Desai understand.

824
01:09:46,665 --> 01:09:48,496
Don't try to act smart.
- Yes.

825
01:09:48,601 --> 01:09:49,568
Go now.
- Yes.

826
01:09:50,636 --> 01:09:51,660
Give this to Chhotya when you meet him.

827
01:09:59,645 --> 01:10:01,738
Sir, I will tell you one thing.

828
01:10:02,848 --> 01:10:03,837
I am not Mr. Desai.

829
01:10:05,317 --> 01:10:06,409
I am Mr. Sheikh.

830
01:10:09,288 --> 01:10:11,449
Sheikh? Then why did you lie?

831
01:10:12,424 --> 01:10:16,087
I did not lie. My name is Sameer Sheikh.

832
01:10:16,662 --> 01:10:18,755
And she is my wife Anuradha Desai.

833
01:10:19,665 --> 01:10:24,193
Now, I know why you act so smart.

834
01:10:24,436 --> 01:10:25,300
Come on, go now.

835
01:10:25,404 --> 01:10:26,632
Yes, we are going.

836
01:10:26,705 --> 01:10:28,434
Go straight to Pakistan

837
01:10:29,475 --> 01:10:31,443
Come on, now wind up.

838
01:10:32,344 --> 01:10:33,333
Why did you do that?

839
01:10:37,383 --> 01:10:41,285
It just feels good. Very good.

840
01:10:52,064 --> 01:10:53,326
Uncle Yusuf.

841
01:10:55,134 --> 01:10:57,728
Mohsin. What are you doing here?

842
01:10:59,371 --> 01:11:01,134
Come. Careful.

843
01:11:03,242 --> 01:11:06,211
You said that father will
come to the camp to fetch me.

844
01:11:06,378 --> 01:11:12,283
But he didn't come.
- How did you come here?

845
01:11:12,418 --> 01:11:16,377
I ran away from the camp alone.
- Mad boy.

846
01:11:18,057 --> 01:11:22,050
You shouldn't roam alone
at night. Come. Sit.

847
01:11:22,995 --> 01:11:24,929
I'll go and drop you. Sit.

848
01:11:31,971 --> 01:11:34,496
Uncle. Give me Suleiman's keys.

849
01:11:38,577 --> 01:11:43,514
I know who broke Suleiman's
shop. They won't escape now.

850
01:11:45,017 --> 01:11:48,953
Don't you understand?
Why do you act so smart?

851
01:11:50,022 --> 01:11:52,923
Will the dead return?

852
01:11:55,160 --> 01:11:56,149
Give me the key.

853
01:12:04,236 --> 01:12:09,105
Wait. Wait. Drop him at
Sabur camp before leaving.

854
01:12:09,308 --> 01:12:10,275
I can't go to the camp now.

855
01:12:10,876 --> 01:12:13,003
Fear God a little. These things..

856
01:12:15,381 --> 01:12:20,182
The poor boy is an orphan.
- Hurry up, then.

857
01:12:21,987 --> 01:12:25,013
Come, Mohsin, he will
drop you at the camp. Okay?

858
01:12:25,491 --> 01:12:28,392
I'll come tomorrow morning to meet.
- With father?

859
01:12:29,695 --> 01:12:32,220
Come. Come dear. Come.

860
01:12:42,675 --> 01:12:44,575
Drop him at the campo first.

861
01:12:50,582 --> 01:12:56,543
I'm very scared.
- Don't worry. We have reached.

862
01:13:00,526 --> 01:13:03,393
Wait. - Come, come.
- Open the boot.

863
01:13:04,964 --> 01:13:06,864
Stop. Stop. Park here.

864
01:13:11,971 --> 01:13:14,565
Don't be scared. Do you have
the spot on your forehead?

865
01:13:15,941 --> 01:13:20,605
It's so late. Hanif will kill me.
- Wait, I'll see.. - Hey, come.

866
01:13:20,779 --> 01:13:21,837
Hey, come here. Come this way.

867
01:13:24,850 --> 01:13:26,875
At this time?

868
01:13:26,952 --> 01:13:32,219
Sir.. sir, we are returning
home after applying henna.

869
01:13:32,391 --> 01:13:33,153
License. Show me.

870
01:13:33,258 --> 01:13:35,089
I have. I have my license.

871
01:13:40,466 --> 01:13:41,455
We both had gone.

872
01:13:44,003 --> 01:13:46,062
Okay. Okay. Come on
go. Don't waste time.

873
01:13:46,138 --> 01:13:47,105
Thank you.

874
01:13:55,047 --> 01:13:57,709
Mohsin, come here. Come.

875
01:14:06,392 --> 01:14:08,485
Be careful of the broken glass.

876
01:14:11,096 --> 01:14:15,931
Sit. Silence. Don't do anything here.

877
01:14:45,764 --> 01:14:47,698
Who is it? Who is it?

878
01:14:47,833 --> 01:14:49,801
It's us. Open.
- Munna? - Open.

879
01:14:52,071 --> 01:14:54,062
We have come.
- We've left the rickshaw at the Red Door..

880
01:14:55,340 --> 01:14:56,307
Careful..

881
01:15:10,689 --> 01:15:11,678
Oh, God.

882
01:15:17,763 --> 01:15:19,731
Who is he?
- What can I do?

883
01:15:20,232 --> 01:15:21,324
Uncle Yusuf gave his
responsibility to me.

884
01:15:21,600 --> 01:15:22,760
I have to drop him at the Sabur.

885
01:15:26,171 --> 01:15:28,196
Hey. What is your name?

886
01:15:36,448 --> 01:15:37,710
Where is that pistol? Where is it?

887
01:15:38,717 --> 01:15:41,618
First, remove this garbage, after
that I'll find the secret cabinet.

888
01:15:43,522 --> 01:15:45,615
The rogue Suleiman was very rich.

889
01:15:46,391 --> 01:15:47,415
What's the use of riches?

890
01:15:48,393 --> 01:15:50,293
He fled as soon as the storm started.

891
01:15:50,395 --> 01:15:53,330
He did the right thing. It's
better than living scared here.

892
01:15:53,465 --> 01:15:56,298
That's right.
- You'll say so.

893
01:15:56,401 --> 01:15:58,232
You had run too.

894
01:15:59,271 --> 01:16:01,205
I don't know how you got
comfort among the Hindus.

895
01:16:02,441 --> 01:16:05,274
And you must have got good
comfort among the Muslims.

896
