904
01:16:27,566 --> 01:16:31,559
I thought a lot about
guns, pistols, bombs.

905
01:16:32,971 --> 01:16:34,939
But I was reminded
of my mother the most.

906
01:16:35,841 --> 01:16:36,830
But I couldn't do anything.

907
01:16:37,676 --> 01:16:40,645
My body still reeks of burnt corpses.

908
01:16:40,946 --> 01:16:43,972
I dream of blood. Their
burnt pieces of flesh..

909
01:16:44,116 --> 01:16:45,947
