01:17:35,067 --> 01:17:36,056
Yes.

916
01:17:36,168 --> 01:17:38,159
It seems small, but it's real.

917
01:17:40,505 --> 01:17:43,406
Be careful. It may contain bullets.
- Open and see.

918
01:17:44,543 --> 01:17:45,532
See.

919
01:17:52,150 --> 01:17:54,141
It doesn't contain anything.

920
01:18:23,582 --> 01:18:33,685
They stabbed the boy and they
pulled the girl by her hair.

921
01:18:33,825 --> 01:18:37,488
And I came running here.

922
01:18:37,829 --> 01:18:41,856
Children are dying of hunger.

923
01:18:46,905 --> 01:18:48,930
