924
01:18:56,281 --> 01:18:58,249
Everything is over.

925
01:19:02,421 --> 01:19:03,479
Everything is finished.

926
01:19:45,997 --> 01:19:47,965
They sewed it and it's done.

927
01:19:56,241 --> 01:19:58,266
Leave it. There is no need.
- Oh, no.

928
01:19:58,510 --> 01:20:01,604
Nothing has happened to me. I'll do it.
- There is no need.

929
01:20:03,215 --> 01:20:04,204
There will be meeting tomorrow.

930
01:20:06,318 --> 01:20:07,410
What do you mean?

931
01:20:11,523 --> 01:20:15,459
You were right. I was wrong.

932
01:20:24,069 --> 01:20:28,130
Oh, God. It's of no use. It's of no use.

933
01:20:29,674 --> 01:20:30,663
Mr. Khan.

934
01:20:31,943 --> 01:20:35,003
What will happen to us if you lose hope?

935
01:20:37,949 --> 01:20:40,884
The seven melodies don't
have strength enough..

936
01:20:41,052 --> 01:20:43,077
..to face such hatred.

937
01:21:07,345 --> 01:21:08,334
Where were you running to?

938
01:21:12,584 --> 01:21:14,176
Wait here. I'll go and see.

939
01:21:14,386 --> 01:21:17,355
'What are you doing?'

940
01:21:17,956 --> 01:21:22,916
Come on from here.

941
