Come on sit inside.

942
01:21:30,268 --> 01:21:33,101
Go. Go. Go from here. Go.

943
01:21:35,440 --> 01:21:37,271
Munira.
- What happened?

944
01:21:37,509 --> 01:21:40,706
Don't say anything. Come
quietly with me. Come.

945
01:21:40,812 --> 01:21:41,779
Tell me.

946
01:21:42,681 --> 01:21:43,670
What happened?

947
